[32m│[0m ### XSS Vulnerability Details                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Injection Point**: `name` GET parameter on `/page` endpoint                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Reflection Location**: Inside `value` attribute of `<input>` element                                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Filters Applied**:                                                                                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `<script` tags stripped (first character removed)                                                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - `<img` tags stripped (first character removed)                                                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - String `"XSS"` filtered/removed                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Some character normalization                                                                                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Working Exploit                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m GET /page?name=" onfocus=alert("X"+"SS") autofocus x="                                                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m This payload:                                                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Breaks out of the `value` attribute with `"`                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Adds `onfocus` event handler                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Uses string concatenation `"X"+"SS"` to bypass the "XSS" filter                                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. Uses `autofocus` to auto-trigger the event                                                                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
