[32m│[0m **Endpoint Analyzed**: `/page?name=` parameter on http://127.0.0.1:32919                                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability Category**: Reflected Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) with aggressive filtering                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Filter Behavior Discovered**:                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **Primary Filter**: Removes `<S` and `<I` patterns (case-insensitive) - including `<script`, `<svg`, `<img`, and their closing equivalents        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **Input Context**: Reflected inside HTML attribute: `value="[INPUT]"`                                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **Quoting Behavior**: Double quotes (`"`) and angle brackets (`>`) are NOT filtered or escaped                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. **Attribute Breakout**: `">` successfully breaks out of the value attribute and injects content into HTML body                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Key Observations**:                                                                                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Normal text, quotes, parentheses, single quotes - all allowed                                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The word "script" alone is NOT filtered                                                                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Angle brackets alone `<>` are NOT filtered                                                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The patterns `<s` and `<i` (any case) trigger the filter                                                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Mixed case does NOT bypass the filter                                                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                                                                                                      [32m│[0m
